{"type": "article", "id": 25303, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-04-12T06:35:06Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 26109, "name": "Alfredo Häberli"}, {"id": 26110, "name": "Stellar Works"}, {"id": 26080, "name": "PINK"}, {"id": 26111, "name": "David Rockwell"}, {"id": 26112, "name": "Edgar Yeo"}, {"id": 26113, "name": "Flávia Arantes Jensen"}, {"id": 26114, "name": "Prospero Rasulo"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 26, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607121053xV1geNZScXu62HYn.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Riviera Tables by Alfredo Häberli </h2>\n<p>这组茶几使用了白色的卡拉拉大理石（Carrara marble），用三块经过切割好的板像积木一样拼接。两块十字交叉构成桌腿，上面再扣上一块作为桌面，结构巧妙且方便拆装和运输。一定程度上解决大理石做较大型家具时不易运输的缺陷。此外，茶几简单的形状和白色纹路让茶几显得轻盈而灵活。<a href=\"http://www.alfredo-haeberli.com/work/tables/12-215/riviera_marble_edition\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122233FCc9VBLu5b6ZSyqm.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.67037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122234na0TCmBzve75cqoS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122234ESCdXq2LnjN4pzRl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122235Ahekqf2Sc1nM89oT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222367FKdcDO50bSL3NUA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Valet by David Rockwell &amp; Stellar Works</h2>\n<p>这是美国设计师 David Rockwell 为家具品牌 Stellar Works 设计的家具组，主要使用金属结构、深色的木材和皮革这三种材料制作了 14 件家具，多用在客厅等需要招待客人的环境，能体现出昂贵的价格、精致的做工和实用性。比如斜靠在墙上的金属架子，依次连接了六边形的镜子、一块置物的木板和皮革做的口袋，简洁有序而又有装饰性。旁边的皮凳有一个用皮革做的灵活的口袋，可以用来放杂志或包。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222365uxMjklsLRAm3Se6.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122237coqw0vig1AfbO2RK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.39957265\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122237GOq3jbSeKPgutIlD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222382HO98odeKlsI1Pun.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122238MCEuaqcHeLR9pft0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122239LFEJDOZ29jPrhysU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.40064103\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Magic Air Purifier by Edgar Yeo</h2>\n<p>这是一个空气净化器的概念，是韩国室内设计师 Edgar Yeo 为韩国东洋美吉（TONGYANG MAGIC）设计的，目的是去除厨房里的油烟。净化器的轮廓的类似于戴森的无叶风扇，但它下面有一个扭曲的底座，灵感源于莫比乌斯带，配合内侧一圈霓虹效果的灯，增加了生活的绚丽。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122239RhyrlLx1d8zna7GD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122240XG9Lup3bYdJ4oFIE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122240eqYw13Dh8LvyBJSu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122241Duo7LBFk3CwqWZxl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122241XDEogUiAHLRvJYxG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69238095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>SHOWER-BUNGA by Flávia Arantes Jensen</h2>\n<p>你常常在洗澡时将洗发水和沐浴露放在地上吗？不断的弯腰拿取多少有些不方便吧。来自丹麦的设计师 Flávia Arantes Jensen 就设计了一个挂洗护用品的挂钩，是用硅胶做的，挂钩连接了两圈有弹性的环来固定洗护用品，最大可承担 1.5kg。产品已完成了众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/568728991/bungee-bath-sleek-fun-in-the-shower/description\">这里是众筹链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222412QvZ7xLhG9IgJEDU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.045\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122242E8JgjWHZTIRchprl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.34537037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222421CU8ErmQtNb9BdlI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.06333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122243VGvLWJlOIHrw9F6j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.295\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122243MwgSb2nWDKH0h8xF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.4\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122244Jra7cwZvCAiSVWnp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.415\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Cut &amp; Pod &amp; Track by Prospero Rasulo for Valdama</h2>\n<p>这是一组遵循“少即是多”原理的洗手池设计，水池是圆形或方形的，深度较浅。方形水池边缘保留了直角转折，在内侧经过了些微的倾斜处理，而圆形或椭圆形水池则凸显出水池的流动性，极具几何感。水龙头分为在水池外或水池中两种，很高，形状也与较规整的几何水池形成对比，突出了水池本身的极简和干净。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122244ytm08BxkgHpDZ7ue.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122244Gk4fF6lSEsq2btgR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222452TjKvcSPxiuLMwAH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222451dja8DQZCb9GWMcs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.83055556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122246wGuH13ZvYqFPdRgi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64305556\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122246Du4GcftXOvgp8zh6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Christian Louboutin by Pink</h2>\n<p>这是法国高跟鞋品牌 Christian Louboutin（克里斯提·鲁布托）推出的礼盒装指甲油系列。他们最开始为蓝、白、黄三种颜色的指甲油设计了黄蓝色的包装。蓝色和黄色像颜料一样随意点缀在包装上，鲜艳而有张力。他们后来增加了另外两种是夏威夷风格的热带植物和芙蓉花，只在背景有白色或黑色的区别，很应景。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122247cfOo9QntarJuVGlE.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.67037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071222473Nv2KwD08VbliBkd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122248jmtIr6KTz41GO7go.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122248YAa6SvH9QC3wyDku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607122249wfzvexYUyscHoTRn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.504\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}